snippet.title: Infinifactory, by Zachtronics
snippet.description:
ESRB Rating: TEEN with Blood and Gore, Language, Mild Sexual Themes, Mild Violence

Now available on Steam! http://store.steampowered.com/app/300570

Infinifactory is a sandbox puzzle game by Zachtronics, the creators of SpaceChem and Infiniminer. Build factories that assemble products for your alien overlords, and try not to die in the process.
